name: 1976-07-18 SET 1 ORPHEUM THEATER San Francisco, CA
description:
I collected these cassettes in the 1980s. I still have them to this day. One day, I might not have the room for them, but with this Augmented Reality collection,  I'll still be able to look at them and remember the good times we had.
